ItemMaster,is,a,source,for,product,images,and,data,The,site,aims,to,provide,free,detailed,information,about,products,so,that,all,vendors,have,the,same,information,available,The,ItemMaster,API,allows,users,access,to,the,ItemMaster,database,so,they,can,make,calls,to,return,a,listing,of,manufacturers,listing,of,brand,names,and,a,listing,of,items,The,API,uses,REST,calls,returns,JSON,or,XML,and,requires,SSL,to,be,used,for,all,calls,to,the,API